## Development Workflow

This project uses [Chama](https://github.com/rafaelportugal/chama) for SDLC orchestration.

Available commands:
- `/chama-ideas` — Brainstorm and create structured ideas (stored as GitHub Issues)
- `/chama-architect` — Transform an idea into RFC + implementation phases
- `/chama-code` — Execute the next task from the backlog
- `/chama-review-loop` — Process PR review comments in a loop

